    "headline": "Road Accidents in Reykjavík Halved Over Past 15 Years",
    "lede": "In Reykjavík, road safety has seen commendable progress. The number of traffic accidents has dropped by nearly half since the early 2000s, showing a significant improvement in driver safety and awareness.",
